[The state of Massachusetts can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at http://healthmap.org/r/3mzB. A county map can be seen at http://geology.com/county-map/massachusetts.shtml- Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ

The overwhelming message is, vaccinate your animals. Protect your environment from forming mosquito breeding grounds. It takes a bit of looking for the constantly present puddle that can be a haven for mosquito larvae, but ridding your area of those is critically important.

Take care to use mosquito repellent for yourself and the appropriate repellent for your animals. - Mod.TG]
